text: Famous Amos has always been my favourite & I always choose their Cookie Cake for any special occasions. Jurong Point Famous Amos never disappoint me with their service & special thanks to Nana Norish for doing my Cookie Cake! ‚ù§Ô∏è
Super friendly staff and my cookie cake turn out really cute ü•∞ bought it for my bf for valentines! thank you so much!

I make this sweet stop every time I am in Singapore, which is becoming more and more often.  I signed up as a member awhile back and had a lovely surprise when I bought a couple of cookie bags yesterday.  As a member, I was gifted a box with 200g cookies on my birthday month.  Thank you for this figuratively and literally sweet gesture!

Lovely staffs advised the best type of gift sets I should purchase to suit my needs! Thank you for being so patient and friendly even though I came so close to closing time! Also really appreciate that all my gifts were prepared very carefully! Definitely coming back! :)

Love the new soft serve concept!
The cookie sauce is so delish!!
Downside I experienced was that two out of three cookie crumbs were either empty or barely any left (like not even one table spoon left). It's an additional $2 for self service toppings and it'd be nice to check and replenish lacking ones.

Will go back for the cookie sauce üòÇ
